snippet.title: Magic to Master - High Scale Playtest [DEBUG]
snippet.description:
Dear community, we present to you the first high-scale gameplay test video of the game. The video is not representative of the final game, but was taken in DEBUG mode. The numbers that remain fixed on the screen are not present in the current game version.

Developer: Laniatus Game LLC.
Publishers: Laniatus Game LLC.
Platforms: Microsoft Windows, Linux, MacOS, Oculus VR
Genres: Massively multiplayer online role-playing game, Free to play, Action game, Massively Multiplayer, Adventure

Official Page: https://www.laniatusgames.com/
Discord Community Channel: https://discord.gg/magictomaster
